3) Key Changes from AM-ETB v0.3

- re-structuring of code and runtime data
- parameterized the implementation and added central parameter definition file param.pl
- added to Assurance Tool an extensible command line interface with checking and help
- added optional command line arguments to Assurance Tool invocation from shell
- examples included as predefined command procedures
- groundwork for background server
- update of READMEs and additional documentation provided as a User Manual (in progress)

