3) Known limitations

- Error handling is rudimentary at present - some error log 
  constructed, and command failures are reported, but error handling
  needs to be more thorough and tested.

- Agents for evidence creation/validation are limited to simple examples.
  These need to be extended for evidence categories and evidence-generating
  tools to be applied.

- Model example is limited.

- Assurance case patterns need to be added for new assurance methodologies.

